{"tid":1379514,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［千祈唔好試系列］嗰日我同我老母一個用殺蟲水一個用電蚊拍殺曱甴，差啲燒咗成間屋","createTime":"2019-07-28T20:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T18:26:39.000Z","uid":25290,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"daa32d558999b7f4b116fd06558ded609020420c","tid":1379514,"uid":25290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:04:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">家居小常識</span><br />\n<br />\n話說嗰日有隻<span style=\"font-size: large;\">陰囊咁大</span>嘅曱甴入撚咗屋，<br />\n屌你即刻嚇到條鳩仲細過撚個陰囊，<br />\n我老母見到即刻攞起個拍拍佢老母<br />\n係呢個時候，屌佢突然起飛，飛得仲快過武力清場，<br />\n仲爬撚咗入我老母件衫度<br />\n<br />\n呢刻，<br />\n我居然喚起小時警惡懲奸嘅夢想，攞起支殺蟲水當係胡椒咁噴佢老母（原來都係噴緊我老母，不過我咁撚弱智點分呢）<br />\n<br />\n嘩我一噴落去，我老母又同時間好似威廉絲兩姊妹一齊上身咁拍落去隻曱甴度，<br />\n一通電，成個電蚊拍燒撚著咗，<br />\n&ldquo;foaum&rdquo;咗一聲，成塊面好似烘三文治咁熱，<br />\n倏爾電火即逝，<br />\n萬物俱靜，<br />\n驚警，害蟊死<br />\n<br />\n蟲屍好似日本燒烤咁掛咗喺個蚊網上面<br />\n成間屋<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n好撚柒臭<br />\n<br />\n然後我睇返，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我咁做好危險，真係唔好亂嚟</span></span>，有班傻閪鬼佬掉殺蟲水入火堆，就好似下面咁，<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IdM_Q3E_pWg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIdM_Q3E_pWg&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4ZyywESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=e5afd2a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IdM_Q3E_pWg</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T4fffaA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT4fffaA.png&h=dc9cc9c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又或者，屌呢條戇鳩仲痴撚線，放個火機喺前面，<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/k2sC29_XR88n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fk2sC29_XR88n&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4ZyywESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=e17f2156\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/k2sC29_XR88n</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nahhtvE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnahhtvE.png&h=652f5b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上次戇鳩鳩死唔去算我好彩，你哋喺屋企咪撚柒試，實燒屋冚家剷。<br />\n<br />\n聽到未<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咪亂試<br />\n咪亂試<br />\n咪亂試</span>"},{"pid":"e2b80905a85e2eb72d685c977e77791cf9597ba8","tid":1379514,"uid":25290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:06:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74e19c2b37b49e4a61f2f220174503db6ebd25f9","tid":1379514,"uid":260201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:08:44.000Z","msg":"10/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d073caaaa94314eb02e81987bccc340b1830ed4","tid":1379514,"uid":25290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:13:05.000Z","msg":"居家知識個個都要知道"},{"pid":"dc366c5b6316ae706eed9ae3026c405c1344ddce","tid":1379514,"uid":91967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea536c7fe3c185e55b971e8487ef7df90f44b9fe","tid":1379514,"uid":180429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:21:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c850fe2096ed957c06cb4e550aaa5c9257dacadb","tid":1379514,"uid":231975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:25:06.000Z","msg":"我無野講！"},{"pid":"d99d243fe90effd21a9b9bd43648aa0ccf42a7a7","tid":1379514,"uid":43398,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b7ad3bbd9084b50c4c3a5cb4d7503e2d64cadd","tid":1379514,"uid":180429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:57:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8d20785e8fd43227af59400f2d2014c48c97693","tid":1379514,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:58:21.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"eb26b578b5cd67d4766e5b6b63da1e50ab5e4aef","tid":1379514,"uid":138734,"like